Package: methPLIER
Type: Package
Title: DNA methylation data analysis tool with non-negative matrix factoriztion
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ken Takasawa
Maintainer: Ken Takasawa <ktakazaw@ncc.go.jp>
Description: The "methPLIER" is a set of packages for DNA methylome data analyzing by non-negative matrix factorization (NMF) with knowledge-matrix constrains. This package provide producing loading matrix B and heatmap plotting.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), PLIER (>= 0.99.0), tidyverse (>= 1.3.1)
Imports: survival (>= 3.3-1), ComplexHeatmap (>= 2.10.0),
    Gviz (>= 1.38.4), lattice (>= 0.20-45), ggtree (>= 3.2.1), 
    ggnewscale (>= 0.4.7), survminer (>= 0.4.9), RColorBrewer (>= 1.1-3),
    GenomeInfoDb (>= 1.30.1)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
VignetteBuilder: knitr
